 0419:     """
 0420:     Susceptible, Infected, Removed (SIR)
 0421:     
 0422:     * Ia: asymptomatic
 0423:     * Is: symptomatic 
 0424:     .. math::
 0425:         \dot{S_{i}}=-\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}
 0426:     .. math::
 0427:         \dot{I}_{i}^{a} = \\alpha_{i}\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}-\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a},
 0428:     .. math::
 0429:         \dot{I}_{i}^{s}= \\bar{\\alpha_{i}}\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}-\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s},
 0430:     .. math::
 0431:         \dot{R}_{i}=\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a}+\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s}.
 0432:     .. math::
 0433:         \lambda_{i}(t)=\\beta\sum_{j=1}^{M}\left(C_{ij}^{a}(t)\\frac{I_{j}^{a}}{N_{j}}+C_{ij}^{s}(t)
 0434:         \\frac{I_{j}^{s}}{N_{j}}\\right),\quad i,j=1,\ldots M
 0435: 
 0436:     ...
 0437: 
 0438:     Parameters
 0439:     ----------
 0440:     parameters: dict
 0441:         Contains the following keys:
 0442: 
 0443:         alpha: float, np.array (M,)
 0444:             Fraction of infected who are asymptomatic.
 0445:         beta: float, np.array (M,)
 0446:             Rate of spread of infection.
 0447:         gIa: float, np.array (M,)
 0448:             Rate of removal from asymptomatic individuals.
 0449:         gIs: float, np.array (M,)
 0450:             Rate of removal from symptomatic individuals.
 0451:         fsa: float, np.array (M,)
 0452:             Fraction by which symptomatic individuals self isolate.
 0453:     M: int
 0454:         Number of compartments of individual for each class.
 0455:         I.e len(contactMatrix)
 0456:     Ni: np.array(M, )
 0457:         Initial number in each compartment and class
 0458:     
 0459:     Examples
 0460:     --------
 0461:     An example of the SIR class  
 0462: 
 0463:     >>> M = 1                   # SIR model with no age structure
 0464:     >>> Ni = 1000*np.ones(M)    # only one age group
 0465:     >>> N = np.sum(Ni)          # total population 
 0466:     >>> 
 0467:     >>> beta  = 0.2             # Infection rate
 0468:     >>> gIa   = 0.1             # Removal rate of asymptomatic infectives
 0469:     >>> gIs   = 0.1             # Removal rate of symptomatic infectives
 0470:     >>> alpha = 0               # Fraction of asymptomatic infectives
 0471:     >>> fsa   = 1               # self-isolation of symtomatic infectives
 0472:     >>> 
 0473:     >>> Ia0 = np.array([0])     # Intial asymptomatic infectives
 0474:     >>> Is0 = np.array([1])     # Initial symptomatic
 0475:     >>> R0  = np.array([0])     # No removed individuals initially
 0476:     >>> S0  = N-(Ia0+Is0+R0)    # S + Ia + Is + R = N
 0477:     >>> 
 0478:     >>> # there is no contact structure
 0479:     >>> def contactMatrix(t):
 0480:     >>>     return np.identity(M)
 0481:     >>> 
 0482:     >>> # duration of simulation and data file
 0483:     >>> Tf = 160;  Nt=160;
 0484:     >>> 
 0485:     >>> # instantiate model
 0486:     >>> parameters = {'alpha':alpha, 'beta':beta, 'gIa':gIa, 'gIs':gIs,'fsa':fsa}
 0487:     >>> model = pyross.deterministic.SIR(parameters, M, Ni)
 0488:     >>> 
 0489:     >>> # simulate model using two possible ways

 0601:     """
 0602:     Susceptible, Infected, Removed (SIkR). Method of k-stages of I
 0603: 
 0604:     .. math::
 0605:         \dot{S_{i}}=-\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i},

 0611:         \dot{R}_{i}=k_{I}\gamma_{I}I_{i}^{k}.
 0612: 
 0613:     .. math::
 0614:         \lambda_{i}(t)=\\beta\sum_{j=1}^{M}\sum_{n=1}^{k}C_{ij}(t)\\frac{I_{j}^{n}}{N_{j}},
 0615:     ...
 0616:

 0618:     ----------

 0734:     """
 0735:     Susceptible, Exposed, Infected, Removed (SEIR)
 0736: 
 0737:     * Ia: asymptomatic
 0738:     * Is: symptomatic 
 0739:      
 0740:     .. math::
 0741:         \dot{S_{i}}=-\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}
 0742:     .. math::
 0743:         \dot{E}_{i}=\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}-\gamma_{E}E_{i}
 0744:     .. math::
 0745:         \dot{I}_{i}^{a} = \\alpha_{i}\gamma_{E}^{i}E_{i}-\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a},
 0746:     .. math::
 0747:         \dot{I}_{i}^{s}= \\bar{\\alpha_{i}}\gamma_{E}^{i}E_{i}-\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s},
 0748:     .. math::
 0749:         \dot{R}_{i}=\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a}+\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s}.
 0750:     .. math::
 0751:         \lambda_{i}(t)=\\beta\sum_{j=1}^{M}\left(C_{ij}^{a}(t)\\frac{I_{j}^{a}}{N_{j}}+C_{ij}^{s}(t)
 0752:         \\frac{I_{j}^{s}}{N_{j}}\\right),\quad i,j=1,\ldots M
 0753: 
 0754: 
 0755:     ...
 0756: 
 0757:     Parameters
 0758:     ----------
 0759:     parameters: dict
 0760:         Contains the following keys:
 0761: 
 0762:         alpha: float, np.array (M,)
 0763:             Fraction of infected who are asymptomatic.
 0764:         beta: float, np.array (M,)
 0765:             Rate of spread of infection.
 0766:         gE: float, np.array (M,)
 0767:             Rate of removal from exposed individuals.
 0768:         gIa: float, np.array (M,)
 0769:             Rate of removal from asymptomatic individuals.
 0770:         gIs: float, np.array (M,)
 0771:             Rate of removal from symptomatic individuals.
 0772:         fsa: float, np.array (M,)
 0773:             Fraction by which symptomatic individuals self isolate.
 0774:     M: int
 0775:         Number of compartments of individual for each class.
 0776:         I.e len(contactMatrix)
 0777:     Ni: np.array(M, )
 0778:         Initial number in each compartment and class
 0779:     """
 0780:

 0891:     """
 0892:     Susceptible, Exposed, Infected, Removed (SEkIkR). 
 0893:     Method of k-stages of E and I
 0894:     
 0895:     .. math::
 0896:         \dot{S_{i}}=-\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i},
 0897:     .. math::
 0898:         \dot{E}_{i}^{1}=\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}-k_{E}\gamma_{E}E_{i}^{1}
 0899:     .. math::
 0900:         \dot{E}_{i}^{k}=k_{E}\gamma_{E}E_{i}^{k-1}-k_{E}\gamma_{E}E_{i}^{k}
 0901:     .. math::
 0902:         \dot{I}_{i}^{1}=k_{E}\gamma_{E}E_{i}^{k}-k_{I}\gamma_{I}I_{i}^{1},
 0903:     .. math::
 0904:         \dot{I}_{i}^{k}=k_{I}\gamma_{I}I_{i}^{(k-1)}-k_{I}\gamma_{I}I_{i}^{k}, 
 0905:     .. math::
 0906:         \dot{R}_{i}=k_{I}\gamma_{I}I_{i}^{k}.
 0907: 
 0908:     .. math::
 0909:         \lambda_{i}(t)=\\beta\sum_{j=1}^{M}\sum_{n=1}^{k}C_{ij}(t)\\frac{I_{j}^{n}}{N_{j}},
 0910:     ...
 0911: 
 0912:     Parameters
 0913:     ----------
 0914:     parameters: dict
 0915:         Contains the following keys:
 0916: 
 0917:         beta: float
 0918:             Rate of spread of infection.
 0919:         gI: float
 0920:             Rate of removal from infected individuals.
 0921:         gE: float
 0922:             Rate of removal from exposed individuals.
 0923:         kI: int
 0924:             number of stages of infectives.
 0925:         kE: int
 0926:             number of stages of exposed.
 0927:     M: int
 0928:         Number of compartments of individual for each class.
 0929:         I.e len(contactMatrix)
 0930:     Ni: np.array(M, )
 0931:         Initial number in each compartment and class
 0932:     """
 0933:

 1053:     """
 1054:     Susceptible, Exposed, Infected, Removed (SEkIkR). 
 1055:     Method of k-stages of E, Ia, and Is
 1056:     
 1057:     * Ia: asymptomatic
 1058:     * Is: symptomatic
 1059:     .. math::
 1060:         \dot{S_{i}}=-\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i},
 1061:     .. math::
 1062:         \dot{E}_{i}^{1}=\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}-k_{E}\gamma_{E}E_{i}^{1}
 1063:     .. math::
 1064:         \dot{E}_{i}^{k_{E}}=k_{E}\gamma_{E}E_{i}^{k_{E}-1}-k_{E}\gamma_{E}E_{i}^{k_{E}}
 1065:     .. math::
 1066:         \dot{I}_{i}^{a1}=\\alpha_{i}k_{E}\gamma_{E}E_{i}^{k}-k_{I}\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a1},
 1067:     .. math::
 1068:         \dot{I}_{i}^{ak_{I}}=k_{I^{a}}\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a(k_{I}-1)}-k_{I}\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{ak_{I}},
 1069:     .. math::
 1070:         \dot{I}_{i}^{s1}=\\bar{\\alpha_{i}}k_{E}\gamma_{E}E_{i}^{k_{E}}-k_{I}\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{a1},
 1071:     .. math::
 1072:         \dot{I}_{i}^{sk_{I}}=k_{I}\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s(k_{I}-1)}-k_{I}\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{sk_{I}},
 1073:     .. math::
 1074:         \dot{R}_{i}=k_{I}\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{ak_{I}}+k_{I}\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{sk_{I}}.
 1075:     
 1076:     .. math::
 1077:         \lambda_{i}(t)=\\beta\sum_{j=1}^{M}\sum_{n=1}^{k_{I}}\left(C_{ij}^{a}
 1078:         \\frac{I_{j}^{an}}{N_{j}}+C_{ij}^{s}\\frac{I_{j}^{sn}}{N_{j}}\\right),
 1079:     ...
 1080: 
 1081:     Parameters
 1082:     ----------
 1083:     parameters: dict
 1084:         Contains the following keys:
 1085: 
 1086:         alpha: float
 1087:             Fraction of infected who are asymptomatic.
 1088:         beta: float
 1089:             Rate of spread of infection.
 1090:         gIa: float
 1091:             Rate of removal from asymptomatic infected individuals.
 1092:         gIs: float
 1093:             Rate of removal from symptomatic infected individuals.
 1094:         gE: float
 1095:             Rate of removal from exposed individuals.
 1096:         kI: int
 1097:             number of stages of asymptomatic infectives.
 1098:         kI: int
 1099:             number of stages of symptomatic infectives.
 1100:         kE: int
 1101:             number of stages of exposed.
 1102:     M: int
 1103:         Number of compartments of individual for each class.
 1104:         I.e len(contactMatrix)
 1105:     Ni: np.array(M, )
 1106:         Initial number in each compartment and class
 1107:     """
 1108:

 1247:     """
 1248:     Susceptible, Exposed, Infected, Removed (SEI8R)
 1249:     The infected class has 8 groups:
 1250: 
 1251:     * Ia: asymptomatic
 1252:     * Is: symptomatic
 1253:     * Ih: hospitalized
 1254:     * Ic: ICU
 1255:     * Im: Mortality
 1256: 
 1257:     .. math::
 1258:         \dot{S_{i}}=-\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}+\sigma_{i},
 1259:     .. math::
 1260:         \dot{E}_{i}=\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}-\gamma_{E}E_{i},
 1261:     .. math::
 1262:         \dot{A}_{i}=\gamma_{E}E_{i}-\gamma_{A}A_{i}
 1263:     .. math::
 1264:         \dot{I}_{i}^{a}=\\alpha_{i}\gamma_{A}A_{i}-\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a},
 1265:     .. math::
 1266:         \dot{I}_{i}^{s}=\\bar{\\alpha_{i}}\gamma_{A}A_{i}-\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s},
 1267:     .. math::
 1268:         \dot{I}_{i}^{s'}=\\bar{h}_{i}\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s}-\gamma_{I^{s'}}I_{i}^{s'}
 1269:     .. math::
 1270:         \dot{I}_{i}^{h}=h_{i}\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s}-\gamma_{I^{h}}I_{i}^{h},
 1271:     .. math::
 1272:         \dot{I}_{i}^{h'}=\\bar{c}_{i}\gamma_{I^{h}}I_{i}^{h}-\gamma_{I^{h'}}I_{i}^{h'},
 1273:     .. math::
 1274:         \dot{I}_{i}^{c}=c_{i}\gamma_{I^{h}}I_{i}^{h}-\gamma_{I^{c}}I_{i}^{c},
 1275:     .. math::
 1276:         \dot{I}_{i}^{c'}=\\bar{m}_{i}\gamma_{I^{c}}I_{i}^{c}-\gamma_{I^{c'}}I_{i}^{c'},
 1277:     .. math::
 1278:         \dot{I}_{i}^{m}=m_{i}\gamma_{I^{c}}I_{i}^{c},
 1279:     .. math::
 1280:         \dot{N}_{i}=\sigma_{i}-m_{i}\gamma_{I^{c}}I_{i}^{c}
 1281:     .. math::
 1282:         \dot{R}_{i}=\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a}+\gamma_{I^{s'}}I_{i}^{s'}+\gamma_{I^{h'}}I_{i}^{h'}+\gamma_{I^{c'}}I_{i}^{c'}.
 1283:     
 1284:     .. math::
 1285:         \lambda_{i}(t)=\\beta\sum_{j=1}^{M}\left(C_{ij}^{a}\\frac{I_{j}^{a}}{N_{j}}+
 1286:         +C_{ij}^{s}\\frac{I_{j}^{s}}{N_{j}}
 1287:         +C_{ij}^{s}\\frac{I_{j}^{s'}}{N_{j}}
 1288:         \\right),
 1289:     ...
 1290: 
 1291:     Parameters
 1292:     ----------
 1293:     parameters: dict
 1294:         Contains the following keys:
 1295: 
 1296:         alpha: float, np.array (M,)
 1297:             Fraction of infected who are asymptomatic.
 1298:         beta: float
 1299:             Rate of spread of infection.
 1300:         gE: float
 1301:             Rate of removal from exposeds individuals.
 1302:         gIa: float
 1303:             Rate of removal from asymptomatic individuals.
 1304:         gIs: float
 1305:             Rate of removal from symptomatic individuals.
 1306:         gIsp: float
 1307:             Rate of removal from symptomatic individuals towards buffer.
 1308:         gIh: float
 1309:             Rate of removal for hospitalised individuals.
 1310:         gIhp: float
 1311:             Rate of removal from hospitalised individuals towards buffer.
 1312:         gIc: float
 1313:             Rate of removal for idividuals in intensive care.
 1314:         gIcp: float
 1315:             Rate of removal from ICU individuals towards buffer.
 1316:         fsa: float
 1317:             Fraction by which symptomatic individuals self isolate.
 1318:         sa: float, np.array (M,)
 1319:             Daily arrival of new susceptables.
 1320:         hh: float, np.array (M,)
 1321:             Fraction hospitalised from Is
 1322:         cc: float, np.array (M,)
 1323:             Fraction sent to intensive care from hospitalised.
 1324:         mm: float, np.array (M,)
 1325:             mortality rate in intensive care
 1326:     M: int
 1327:         Number of compartments of individual for each class.

 1522:     """
 1523:     Susceptible, Exposed, Asymptomatic and infected, Infected, Removed (SEAIR)
 1524: 
 1525:     * Ia: asymptomatic
 1526:     * Is: symptomatic
 1527:     * E: exposed
 1528:     * A: asymptomatic and infectious
 1529:     
 1530:     .. math::
 1531:         \dot{S_{i}}=-\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}
 1532:     .. math::
 1533:         \dot{E}_{i}=\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}-\gamma_{E}E_{i}
 1534:     .. math::
 1535:         \dot{A}_{i}=\gamma_{E}E_{i}-\gamma_{A}A_{i}
 1536:     .. math::
 1537:         \dot{I}_{i}^{a}=\\alpha_{i}\gamma_{A}A_{i}-\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a},
 1538:     .. math::
 1539:         \dot{I}_{i}^{s}=\\bar{\\alpha_{i}}\gamma_{A}A_{i}-\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s},
 1540:     .. math::
 1541:         \dot{R}_{i}=\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a}+\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s}.
 1542: 
 1543:     .. math::
 1544:         \lambda_{i}(t)=\\beta\sum_{j=1}^{M}\left(C_{ij}^{a}\\frac{I_{j}^{a}}{N_{j}}+C_{ij}^{a}
 1545:         \\frac{A_{j}}{N_{j}}+C_{ij}^{s}\\frac{I_{j}^{s}}{N_{j}}\\right),
 1546: 
 1547:     ...
 1548: 
 1549:     Parameters
 1550:     ----------
 1551:     parameters: dict
 1552:         Contains the following keys:
 1553: 
 1554:         alpha: float
 1555:             Fraction of infected who are asymptomatic.
 1556:         beta: float
 1557:             Rate of spread of infection.
 1558:         gIa: float
 1559:             Rate of removal from asymptomatic individuals.
 1560:         gIs: float
 1561:             Rate of removal from symptomatic individuals.
 1562:         fsa: float
 1563:             Fraction by which symptomatic individuals self isolate.
 1564:         gE: float
 1565:             Rate of removal from exposeds individuals.
 1566:         gA: float
 1567:             Rate of removal from activated individuals.
 1568:     M: int
 1569:         Number of compartments of individual for each class.
 1570:         I.e len(contactMatrix)
 1571:     Ni: np.array(M, )
 1572:         Initial number in each compartment and class
 1573:     """
 1574:

 1699:     """
 1700:     Susceptible, Exposed, Activated, Infected, Removed (SEAI8R)
 1701:     The infected class has 8 groups:
 1702: 
 1703:     * Ia: asymptomatic
 1704:     * Is: symptomatic
 1705:     * Ih: hospitalized
 1706:     * Ic: ICU
 1707:     * Im: Mortality
 1708: 
 1709:     .. math::
 1710:         \dot{S_{i}}=-\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}+\sigma_{i},
 1711:     .. math::
 1712:         \dot{E}_{i}=\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}-\gamma_{E}E_{i},
 1713:     .. math::
 1714:         \dot{A}_{i}=\gamma_{E}E_{i}-\gamma_{A}A_{i}
 1715:     .. math::
 1716:         \dot{I}_{i}^{a}=\\alpha_{i}\gamma_{A}A_{i}-\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a},
 1717:     .. math::
 1718:         \dot{I}_{i}^{s}=\\bar{\\alpha_{i}}\gamma_{A}A_{i}-\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s},
 1719:     .. math::
 1720:         \dot{I}_{i}^{s'}=\\bar{h}_{i}\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s}-\gamma_{I^{s'}}I_{i}^{s'}
 1721:     .. math::
 1722:         \dot{I}_{i}^{h}=h_{i}\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s}-\gamma_{I^{h}}I_{i}^{h},
 1723:     .. math::
 1724:         \dot{I}_{i}^{h'}=\\bar{c}_{i}\gamma_{I^{h}}I_{i}^{h}-\gamma_{I^{h'}}I_{i}^{h'},
 1725:     .. math::
 1726:         \dot{I}_{i}^{c}=c_{i}\gamma_{I^{h}}I_{i}^{h}-\gamma_{I^{c}}I_{i}^{c},
 1727:     .. math::
 1728:         \dot{I}_{i}^{c'}=\\bar{m}_{i}\gamma_{I^{c}}I_{i}^{c}-\gamma_{I^{c'}}I_{i}^{c'},
 1729:     .. math::
 1730:         \dot{I}_{i}^{m}=m_{i}\gamma_{I^{c}}I_{i}^{c},
 1731:     .. math::
 1732:         \dot{N}_{i}=\sigma_{i}-m_{i}\gamma_{I^{c}}I_{i}^{c}
 1733:     .. math::
 1734:         \dot{R}_{i}=\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a}+\gamma_{I^{s'}}I_{i}^{s'}+\gamma_{I^{h'}}I_{i}^{h'}+\gamma_{I^{c'}}I_{i}^{c'}.
 1735:     
 1736:     .. math::
 1737:         \lambda_{i}(t)=\\beta\sum_{j=1}^{M}\left(C_{ij}^{a}\\frac{I_{j}^{a}}{N_{j}}+C_{ij}^{a}
 1738:         \\frac{A_{j}}{N_{j}}
 1739:         +C_{ij}^{s}\\frac{I_{j}^{s}}{N_{j}}
 1740:         +C_{ij}^{s}\\frac{I_{j}^{s'}}{N_{j}}
 1741:         \\right),
 1742: 
 1743:     ...
 1744: 
 1745:     Parameters
 1746:     ----------
 1747:     parameters: dict
 1748:         Contains the following keys:
 1749: 
 1750:         alpha: float, np.array (M,)
 1751:             Fraction of infected who are asymptomatic.
 1752:         beta: float
 1753:             Rate of spread of infection.
 1754:         gE: float
 1755:             Rate of removal from exposeds individuals.
 1756:         gIa: float
 1757:             Rate of removal from asymptomatic individuals.
 1758:         gIs: float
 1759:             Rate of removal from symptomatic individuals.
 1760:         gIsp: float
 1761:             Rate of removal from symptomatic individuals towards buffer.
 1762:         gIh: float
 1763:             Rate of removal for hospitalised individuals.
 1764:         gIhp: float
 1765:             Rate of removal from hospitalised individuals towards buffer.
 1766:         gIc: float
 1767:             Rate of removal for idividuals in intensive care.
 1768:         gIcp: float
 1769:             Rate of removal from ICU individuals towards buffer.
 1770:         fsa: float
 1771:             Fraction by which symptomatic individuals self isolate.
 1772:         sa: float, np.array (M,)
 1773:             Daily arrival of new susceptables.
 1774:         hh: float, np.array (M,)
 1775:             Fraction hospitalised from Is
 1776:         cc: float, np.array (M,)
 1777:             Fraction sent to intensive care from hospitalised.
 1778:         mm: float, np.array (M,)
 1779:             mortality rate in intensive care
 1780:     M: int
 1781:         Number of compartments of individual for each class.
 1782:         I.e len(contactMatrix)
 1783:     Ni: np.array(M, )
 1784:         Initial number in each compartment and class
 1785:     """

 1981:     """
 1982:     Susceptible, Exposed, Asymptomatic and infected, 
 1983:     Infected, Removed, Quarantined (SEAIRQ)
 1984: 
 1985:     * Ia: asymptomatic
 1986:     * Is: symptomatic
 1987:     * E: exposed
 1988:     * A: asymptomatic and infectious
 1989:     * Q: quarantined 
 1990:  
 1991:     .. math::
 1992:         \dot{S_{i}}=-\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}
 1993:     .. math::
 1994:         \dot{E}_{i}=\lambda_{i}(t)S_{i}-(\gamma_{E}+\\tau_{E})A_{i}
 1995:     .. math::
 1996:         \dot{A}_{i}=\gamma_{E}E_{i}-(\gamma_{A}+\\tau_{A})A_{i}
 1997:     .. math::
 1998:         \dot{I}_{i}^{a}=\\alpha_{i}\gamma_{A}A_{i}-(\gamma_{I^{a}}+\\tau_{I^a})I_{i}^{a},
 1999:     .. math::
 2000:         \dot{I}_{i}^{s}=\\bar{\\alpha_{i}}\gamma_{A}A_{i}-(\gamma_{I^{s}}+\\tau_{I^a})I_{i}^{s},
 2001:     .. math::
 2002:         \dot{R}_{i}=\gamma_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a}+\gamma_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s}.
 2003:     .. math::
 2004:         \dot{Q}_{i}=\\tau_{S}S_{i}+\\tau_{E}E_{i}+\\tau_{A}A_{i}+\\tau_{I^{s}}I_{i}^{s}+\\tau_{I^{a}}I_{i}^{a}
 2005: 
 2006:     .. math::
 2007:         \lambda_{i}(t)=\\beta\sum_{j=1}^{M}\left(C_{ij}^{a}\\frac{I_{j}^{a}}{N_{j}}+C_{ij}^{a}
 2008:         \\frac{A_{j}}{N_{j}}+C_{ij}^{s}\\frac{I_{j}^{s}}{N_{j}}\\right),
 2009: 
 2010: 
 2011:     ...
 2012: 
 2013:     Parameters
 2014:     ----------
 2015:     parameters: dict
 2016:         Contains the following keys:
 2017: 
 2018:         alpha: float
 2019:             Fraction of infected who are asymptomatic.
 2020:         beta: float, np.array (M,)
 2021:             Rate of spread of infection.
 2022:         gIa: float, np.array (M,)
 2023:             Rate of removal from asymptomatic individuals.
 2024:         gIs: float, np.array (M,)
 2025:             Rate of removal from symptomatic individuals.
 2026:         gE: float, np.array (M,)
 2027:             Rate of removal from exposed individuals.
 2028:         gA: float, np.array (M,)
 2029:             Rate of removal from activated individuals.
 2030:         fsa: float, np.array (M,)
 2031:             Fraction by which symptomatic individuals self isolate.
 2032:         tE: float, np.array (M,)
 2033:             testing rate and contact tracing of exposeds
 2034:         tA: float, np.array (M,)
 2035:             testing rate and contact tracing of activateds
 2036:         tIa: float, np.array (M,)

 2874:     Generic user-defined epidemic model with quarantine.
 2875:     ...
 2876: 
 2877:     Parameters
 2878:     ----------
 2879:     model_spec: dict
 2880:         A dictionary specifying the model. See `Examples`.
 2881:     parameters: dict
 2882:         Contains the values for the parameters given in the model specification.
 2883:         All parameters can be float if not age-dependent, and np.array(M,) if age-dependent
 2884:     M: int
 2885:         Number of compartments of individual for each class.
 2886:         I.e len(contactMatrix)
 2887:     Ni: np.array(M, )
 2888:         Initial number in each compartment and class
 2889: 
 2890:     Examples
 2891:     --------
 2892:     An example of model_spec and parameters for SIR class with a constant influx, 
 2893:     random testing (without false positives/negatives), and quarantine
 2894: 
 2895:     >>> model_spec = {
 2896:             "classes" : ["S", "I"],
 2897:             "S" : {
 2898:                 "infection" : [ ["I", "-beta"] ]
 2899:             },

 2901:                 "linear"    : [ ["I", "-gamma"] ],

 2903:             },

 2906:         }

 3197:     """	
 3198:     DEPRECATED.	
 3199:     	
 3200:     Susceptible, Exposed, Infected, Removed (SEI5R)	
 3201:     The infected class has 5 groups:	
 3202:     * Ia: asymptomatic	
 3203:     * Is: symptomatic	
 3204:     * Ih: hospitalized	
 3205:     * Ic: ICU	
 3206:     * Im: Mortality	
 3207:     ...	
 3208:     Parameters	
 3209:     ----------	
 3210:     parameters: dict	
 3211:         Contains the following keys:	
 3212:         alpha: float, np.array (M,)	
 3213:             Fraction of infected who are asymptomatic.	
 3214:         beta: float	
 3215:             Rate of spread of infection.	
 3216:         gE: float	
 3217:             Rate of removal from exposeds individuals.	
 3218:         gIa: float	
 3219:             Rate of removal from asymptomatic individuals.	
 3220:         gIs: float	
 3221:             Rate of removal from symptomatic individuals.	
 3222:         gIh: float	
 3223:             Rate of removal for hospitalised individuals.	
 3224:         gIc: float	
 3225:             Rate of removal for idividuals in intensive care.	
 3226:         fsa: float	
 3227:             Fraction by which symptomatic individuals self isolate.	
 3228:         fh  : float	
 3229:             Fraction by which hospitalised individuals are isolated.	
 3230:         sa: float, np.array (M,)	
 3231:             Daily arrival of new susceptables.	
 3232:         hh: float, np.array (M,)	
 3233:             Fraction hospitalised from Is	
 3234:         cc: float, np.array (M,)	
 3235:             Fraction sent to intensive care from hospitalised.	
 3236:         mm: float, np.array (M,)	
 3237:             mortality rate in intensive care	
 3238:     M: int	
 3239:         Number of compartments of individual for each class.	
 3240:         I.e len(contactMatrix)
